{"tid":1741851,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)懲罰者1-2 從前，有個荷里活","createTime":"2019-11-20T13:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T18:38:55.000Z","uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"910af6289a0d9de17adf478a07afd78c7a38e173","tid":1741851,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:49:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">啊~~~死黑警~~~又唔做嘢又唔讀書</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLG0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=d5b9715f\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLG0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=43863cc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLG0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=2ebd275b\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/c/cf/Punisherwarzoneteaser.jpg/220px-Punisherwarzoneteaser.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fen%2Fthumb%2Fc%2Fcf%2FPunisherwarzoneteaser.jpg%2F220px-Punisherwarzoneteaser.jpg&h=08597fbf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/4/4c/Once_Upon_a_Time_in_Hollywood.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F4%2F4c%2FOnce_Upon_a_Time_in_Hollywood.jpg&h=b86b5b83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.弗蘭克&middot;卡斯特（托馬斯&middot;簡Thomas Jane 飾）的生命中，絕大部分時間都在於死神賽跑。早年在海軍陸戰隊服役，退役後又進入FBI。在槍砲火光中生活了多年之後，弗蘭克不願再整日收到死亡的威脅，家人整日為他擔驚受怕。所以，他決定提前退休與妻兒享受平靜的生活。可是，在最後的一次任務中，卻因意外使一名無辜青年死亡。而這名青年的父親卻是坦帕市的大富商霍華德&middot;桑特（約翰&middot;特拉沃塔John Travolta 飾）。為了給兒子報仇..<br />\n<br />\n2.本想歸隱田園，與家人共度天倫的FBI探員弗蘭克&middot;卡斯特，無奈的在黑幫殺掉妻<br />\n兒之後走向了黑暗復仇的不歸路。弗蘭克&middot;卡斯特大難不死，在悲痛過後開始成為這個城市裡隱秘的&ldquo;懲罰者&rdquo;，在黑暗中打擊那些猖狂的犯罪分子的頭號先鋒。在處決了城內走私行當的龍頭老大之後，懲罰者的名聲鵲起，因此也令城內不少罪犯聞風喪膽，而他也就繼續穿著代表懲罰者的骷髏制服，穿梭在這個充滿罪惡的都市中.....<br />\n<br />\n3.在1969年的洛杉磯，演員瑞克&middot;達爾頓曾憑西部電視劇《賞金律法》（Bounty Law）而當紅一時，但之後因酗酒問題及轉型電影圈的失敗而使他的演藝事業陷入低迷。達爾頓的特技替身演員兼好友克里夫&middot;布茲是一名退役軍人，他和他養的比特犬共同住在凡奈斯附近的一輛廢棄拖車上，他不斷地試圖給予達爾頓鼓勵。與此同時，演員莎朗&middot;蒂和她的導演丈夫羅曼&middot;波蘭斯基剛搬進了達爾頓家的隔壁。達爾頓希望與這對夫婦交朋友，以讓波蘭斯基幫助自己東山再起。 <br />\n<br />\n10 50PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLG0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=30683c53\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLG0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=865146ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9764f0f04ee6f3a501a6dd853c90c2a2f1a5efd","tid":1741851,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56af69b5d9df4ff698eedac39500a7c36bcd7210","tid":1741851,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a335ba2a9ba6c78c7735bf371db7fd9c09219783","tid":1741851,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:28:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f636d7391d3a3c6b7adde7dd01d6167066a350b3","tid":1741851,"uid":318362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T16:29:46.000Z","msg":"Netflix the punisher先好眯"},{"pid":"823b73dd57998da6335dc30ed1a15d2c58cc9b66","tid":1741851,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T18:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}